{{Italic title}}
'''''Annual Review of Resource Economics''''' is a [[Peer review|peer-reviewed]] [[academic journal]] published by [[Annual Reviews]]. It publishes [[systematic review|reviews]] of [[resource economics]] covering such topics as agricultural economics, environmental economics, renewable resources, and exhaustible resource. It was established in 2009 and the current [[editor-in-chief]] is [[Gordon Rausser]].

